data.description: What a great opportunity to own an 8 acre horse property with an arena and endless views offering the most amazing sunsets.  The home has 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, a den and a bonus/workout room.  Full length front covered porch and enclosed back patio/Arizona Room with a nice sized store room.  New Roof in 2021!  New cabinet faces and fresh paint too!
